  <description>
    <p>jdAppStreamEdit (previously known as jdAppdataEdit) allows you to easily create and edit AppStream (.appdata.xml or .metainfo.xml) files for your Application.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Easy to use</li>
      <li>Full support for the Open Age Rating System (OARS)</li>
      <li>The AppStream files are fully translatable</li>
      <li>Releases can be imported from GitHub, GitLab, Gitea, Git Repos and NEWS files</li>
      <li>You can view a preview in Gnome Software</li>
      <li>You can use a existing .desktop file as template</li>
      <li>Supports External Releases</li>
      <li>Plugins</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
